    "content": "<p>Let $$x(t) = 100\\cos (10.5Wt)$$ be passed through an LTI system having  impulse response $$h(t) = \\pi {\\left( {{{\\sin Wt} \\over {\\pi t}}} \\right)^2}\\cos 10Wt$$. The output of the system is</p>",
